article_title: No, Moody's Did Not Downgrade The Health Insurance Sector, But Yes Obamacare Is Squeezing The Industry

article_metadata.author: Carrie Sheffield

og.description: This week Moody’s changed its outlook to “negative” from “stable” for the health insurance industry, and that’s triggered a raft of inaccurate headlines blaring that Moody’s “downgraded” the sector. This also triggered backlash from some on the right who worry this will be politicized by the Obama administration in light [...]
